premise_source_doc_sentence: Jorma Christopher `` Jorm '' Taccone  (  -LSB- ` jɔrmə_tə ` koʊni -RSB- born March 19 , 1977  )  is an American actor , comedian , director , producer , writer , record producer , and musician .
Taccone is one third of the sketch comedy troupe The Lonely Island along with childhood friends Andy Samberg and Akiva Schaffer .
In 2010 , he co-wrote and directed the SNL spin-off film MacGruber , which was his directorial debut .
Taccone directed his second feature with Akiva Schaffer , the musical comedy Popstar : Never Stop Never Stopping , which he also co-wrote and co-starred with Schaffer and Samberg .
The film was released on June 3 , 2016 to positive reviews .
